y":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T03:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/112810_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F112810_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=47300a1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌睇緊屎post,第一眼睇錯做屎"},{"pid":"7c491ea9d59e22116fc1f9fa5b7f2323cdc5975f","tid":701133,"uid":13468,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"beb5f1f3b2053ab39684756e617f7fa0a8c5ca1b","tid":701133,"uid":93986,"like":208,"dislike":1,"score":207,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T01:52:39.000Z","msg":"M據臨床身心行為家李寶能表示，郭羨妮可能心理壓力過大，才會做出小狗大小便佔地盤的行為，嚴重的話可能會導致精神崩潰。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T03:30:08.000Z","msg":"咩撚話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b23edff7ba569a1c29eec7e0b4b23526da9ee5","tid":701133,"uid":22683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"709ad6e846961adf246ca7373470100fc8cc9ec7","tid":701133,"uid":190739,"like":205,"dislike":1,"score":204,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T01:45:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/twapple/640pix/20050913/EN05/EN05_001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2Ftwapple%2F640pix%2F20050913%2FEN05%2FEN05_001.jpg&h=2d9607f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【郭家崴╱綜合報導】溫兆倫前女友、前港姐郭羨妮隨地大小便，被罵沒教養。據新一期《忽然1周》報導，曾是一九九九年香港小姐的郭羨妮，美貌、身材、智慧兼具，卻在上周日被目擊在河南片場隨地大小便。事實上，片場有乾淨的廁所，距離她拍攝的地方不到一分鐘路程，雖說人有三急，但她有廁所不上的荒誕行徑，著實令人不解。<br />\n<br />\n上周日，郭羨妮在河南焦作影城拍攝新戲《爭霸傳奇》，演絕代美女西施，身穿古裝的她和助理四處張望，神神秘秘地走到走廊盡頭隱密處，她的助理左顧右盼似在把風，不消數分鐘，她神色從容走回片場。她在牆邊留下幾堆用紙巾圍起來的「自製便盆」和「黃金」，還沒靠近就有陣陣異味。她上完廁所沒洗手，用手摟著同劇的男演員陳坤，陳坤也緊握她的雙手，兩人溫馨互望，舉動親密又有「味道」。 <br />\n<br />\n被罵沒教養<br />\n隔天，她故技重施，不怕令人作嘔的惡臭，再和助理鬼鬼祟祟走到她的「私家廁所」，助理照樣在附近把風，她小解完地上濕了一片，也招來清潔工怒罵：「真沒教養！」保安人員也斥責：「洗手間很近，隨地拉（屎）要罰款的。」<br />\n郭羨妮當過空姐，身為公眾人物卻隨地解放，經紀人Derek說：「荒郊野外沒廁所，好多人都這樣。」後來得知附近就有廁所，才吞吞吐吐回說：「我現在聯絡不到她，我也想知道發生什麼事？」<br />\n據臨床身心行為家李寶能表示，郭羨妮可能心理壓力過大，才會做出小狗大小便佔地盤的行為，嚴重的話可能會導致精神崩潰。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T03:30:18.000Z","msg":"張相影到好淫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112c9a6e733b8c2e92dddd13eeea376ee1ee24fb","tid":701133,"uid":18246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T03:50:23.000Z","msg":"之前見到啲人話佢係俾人跣<br />\n唔知係咪真"},{"pid":"2f278726a08b2ae998c942d70ba2b65775eef35b","tid":701133,"uid":9887,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T03:51:55.000Z","msg":"當年有冇影個廁所？<br />\n大陸廁所惡劣起上黎唔簡單<br />\n支那人自己都頂唔順所以周街痾"},{"pid":"9176e28ccfeb5ae6c66da75496aa16a371faa0fe","tid":701133,"uid":808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:54:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ade7c04c36e9d9583b8966a9f9b2f61aaa86375","tid":701133,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"4aac61ea5cfb83c200940bbc3b303525a7988b99","tid":701133,"uid":67922,"like":0,"dislike":136,"score":-136,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T03:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/112810_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F112810_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=47300a1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌睇緊屎post,第一眼睇錯做屎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T05:02:07.000Z","msg":"以為自己好撚好笑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00c5af337bb761f7b741afdd63ae220d13b580f","tid":701133,"uid":111002,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"4aac61ea5cfb83c200940bbc3b303525a7988b99","tid":701133,"uid":67922,"like":0,"dislike":136,"sc